Surf_delusion
--------------------
This map has a total of 8 stages,
The order of the stages is completely random.
In the end you will be able to get extra health and spend it on power-ups.
--------------------
The map should be played with "sv_airaccelerate 150" for best results.
--------------------
Please enjoy!
